messages.0: Hi Reuben, my name is Michele and I am interested in staying at your place for 1 day, from 2016-03-31 to 2016-04-01. The calendar is open on these days and I am wondering if it is still available? A little bit more about myself: I am a graduate student from Milan, Italy and study Communication Design. I am fond of exploring cultures and visual arts around the world. Since the trip is coming up very soon, and I found my schedule matches perfectly with the opening in your calendar, I am wondering if you would be willing to lower the rate to $30/night? I would be willing to make the booking immediately if the price is ok with you.
